- If you see errors about `signal` or `computed`, make sure you imported them from `@angular/core`.
- If the favorite button doesn't show, check your CSS – the `position: absolute` might need a parent with `position: relative`. The `.product-item` already has `position: relative` in the CSS I provided, so it should work.
